Pizza-Licious:
The purpose of the app is to create a custom pizza shop that can automate itself. There are 3 different sizes of pizza, 4 types of crust, a choice between Premium Toppings and Regular toppings, etc. The choices are all in the power of the customer.

Screens and feature:
Home Screen: Once the app is opened the user first sees the Home Screen. The screen allows the user the option to create a new order. 
To exit the program the user will press the number 0.